' Consumer for the PKG-02 security fixture: it imports the malicious
' `sec_confused` package whose compiled IR carries a type-confused body (a
' member access on an Integer). The package's signature tables still declare
' `run() AS Integer`, so this consumer type-checks and links; the build must
' fail during IR semantic verification when the body is decoded for native
' lowering, rather than producing an executable.
IMPORT io
IMPORT sec_confused AS sec_confused

FUNC main AS Integer
  io::print(toString(sec_confused::run()))
  RETURN 0
END FUNC
